Susan Hockfield

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Susan Hockfield



Hockfield at the 2012 World Economic Forum Annual Meeting






President of the Massachusetts Institute of Technology


In office
2004–2012


Preceded by
Charles Vest


Succeeded by
L. Rafael Reif





Personal details


Born
(1951-03-24) March 24, 1951 (age 66)
Chicago, Illinois


Spouse(s)
Thomas N. Byrne, M.D


