Susan Hockfield, a distinguished neuroscientist and current provost at Yale University, has been selected the 16th president of the Massachusetts Institute of Technology.Photo / Donna CoveneyFull Screen
 
 





Dr. Susan Hockfield selected 16th president













August 26, 2004




